    <item>
      <title>Education and Training in Food Science and Technology to Enhance Food Security in Developing Nations</title>
      <link>http://knowledge.cta.int/en/Dossiers/S-T-Policy/Reshaping-tertiary-agricultural-education/Feature-articles/Education-and-Training-in-Food-Science-and-Technology-to-Enhance-Food-Security-in-Developing-Nations</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
&lt;div class="clear"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;!-- ****************** Begin image ****************** --&gt;
&lt;table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="200"&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;

&lt;!-- Spacer left --&gt; &lt;!-- End spacer --&gt;

