    <item>
      <title>The Ocean and the Human Family - World Oceans Day 2015 </title>
      <link>http://knowledge.cta.int/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/The-Ocean-and-the-Human-Family-World-Oceans-Day-2015</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Young people up to age 24 can participate in a contest for the Mundus maris Award 2015– We Are All Connected To The Ocean for celebrating the World Oceans Day 2015, 8 June 2015.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
